{"tid":1960475,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【第二胎9月出世】李雨陽小食店一執一退股 蝕咗囝囝3年教育基金","createTime":"2020-04-06T07:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T15:49:27.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"881fb1ea55ed82b8040f8eaee5a766a338301aee","tid":1960475,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T07:45:07.000Z","msg":"世紀疫症武漢肺炎大肆打擊香港經濟，食肆和零售業首當其衝，鄧一君的兩間麵店捱不過疫巿先後執笠，短短年半蝕足200萬。近年轉營開小食店的李雨陽，去年跟友人在11月在深水埗開一間泰式快餐店，近月生意大受疫情影響，他最近決定退股，計埋觀塘廣場上月尾執笠，這幾年轉營搞食店共蝕了約30多萬。已有一名2歲多囝囝李頌天的他，近日又追女成功，太太鄭嘉詠將於9月生B女，李雨陽要積極諗計賺奶粉錢，他暫時手頭只有參與拍攝香港開電視節目《Fit開有條路》。<br />\n<br />\n李雨陽眼見現在疫情嚴峻，食肆生意大受影響，他在元州商場開的新店經營了才4個多月，本也未回，他便決定退股早日離場，李雨陽今日接受《蘋果》電話訪問時說：「我同太太都決定，元州商場間舖都唔做啦，我哋會退出，現有股東頂埋，都搞緊轉名手續。間店仲有開，只係已經唔關我事。」問到可有甚麼打算？李雨陽續說：「而家專心幫開電視做節目，希望做好啲，多啲觀眾支持。」<br />\n<br />\n李雨陽表示一店執，另一店離場，他都蝕大本：「今次都幾入肉，基本冇咗天天（囝囝）嘅3年教育基金，嚟緊天天要返學，學費都甘㗎。」李雨陽短期內都不敢再做生意，他說：「應該唔會啦，除非真係好有緣，另外又有一間舖好抵做，如果唔係都會抱住觀望態度先，等所有問題事情都過去，再搵吓有咩搞。」雖然疫情令李雨陽荷包唔見錢，但他卻仍然樂觀面對：「生活就係咁，唔想嘅嘢都要接受，另一個角度講，我哋叫好彩，都重有本事蝕，所以感恩開電視有工開，如果唔識感恩，唔識喺低谷搵樂趣，做人就好辛苦。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200406/large/1586152390_f2a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200406%2Flarge%2F1586152390_f2a4.jpg&h=bea78f54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200406/large/1586152408_3ff7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200406%2Flarge%2F1586152408_3ff7.jpg&h=820b911d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200406/SIRBLOZSM7SGNGLEC7BUM6XGTY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200406%2FSIRBLOZSM7SGNGLEC7BUM6XGTY%2F&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLQRUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=27545e12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200406%2FSIRBLOZSM7SGNGLEC7BUM6XGTY%2F&h=f50f69ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200406/SIRBLOZSM7SGNGLEC7BUM6XGTY/</a>"},{"pid":"9e41794729cbaf9b115c6d57c393d62074295012","tid":1960475,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T07:51:01.000Z","msg":"藍定黃？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad08a20c4935ce831dc8f9c5f562352ac9c6806","tid":1960475,"uid":186755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:03:32.000Z","msg":"觀塘個間D早餐真係又貴又唔好食...."},{"pid":"fda1ab35570ed58d911a7460b4407425406a16c7","tid":1960475,"uid":255962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:08:28.000Z","msg":"藍<br />\n抵撚死"},{"pid":"936b7f32a360d9210b0bd3391c57ced726d2c7c3","tid":1960475,"uid":68080,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:11:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkleaks.info/data/41587d5fe4592965\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkleaks.info%2Fdata%2F41587d5fe4592965&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLQRUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=26d499db\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkleaks.info/data/41587d5fe4592965</a><br />\n<br />\n李雨陽：「丟盡香港人臉面，不配做炎黃子孫」<br />\n<br />\n抵你死 幾時破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"476cce00eab73a8dd731587e6e3d306693f39e33","tid":1960475,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:13:35.000Z","msg":"深水埗元州商場仲有間<br />\n<br />\n元州邨手足加油 唔好去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0c4ba86b540a75bbdccddde3a357556d419b30","tid":1960475,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"936b7f32a360d9210b0bd3391c57ced726d2c7c3","tid":1960475,"uid":68080,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020